summary: You can now use the chests in the thieves guild safe room
descriptionHtml:
[SPOILER] So Mercer stole everything from the safe-room - you\'re the guild master I\'m sure its not beyond you\'re capabilities to close the lids on those chests and start filling them up with others hard earned valuables. [/SPOILER]

Replaces all the static always open chests that you couldn\'t put anything in with non-respawning player chests designed to store all that loot that you would accumulate from a successful career of larceny and general lawlessness.
author: Dan L33
